es — not tropical ones!\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4\",\"type\":\"odd-one-out\",\"questionText\":\"Which one does NOT grow on a bush?\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4-a\",\"text\":\"Gooseberry\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4-b\",\"text\":\"Blackberry\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4-c\",\"text\":\"Date\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4-d\",\"text\":\"Blueberry\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null}],\"correctOptionId\":\"gooseberry-q4-c\",\"explanationCorrect\":\"Yes! Date grows on a palm tree, not a bush!\",\"explanationIncorrect\":\"Hmm, Date is the odd one out — it grows on a palm tree!\"}],\"surpriseFact\":\"Gooseberry pie is one of the oldest recorded recipes in Britain!\",\"difficulty\":\"medium\"},{\"id\":\"dragon-fruit\",\"name\":\"Dragon Fruit\",\"image\":\"/images/catalogue/dragon-fruit.webp\",\"category\":\"berry\",\"subcategory\":\"exotic\",\"colours\":[\"pink\",\"red\",\"white\"],\"growsOn\":\"vine\",\"origin\":\"Central America\",\"season\":\"summer\",\"funFacts\":[{\"text\":\"I have bright pink skin with green scales like a dragon!\",\"highlightWord\":\"scales\",\"factType\":\"colour\"},{\"text\":\"I grow on a type of cactus that climbs like a vine!\",\"highlightWord\":\"cactus\",\"factType\":\"growth\"},{\"text\":\"I only bloom at night — my flowers are closed by morning!\",\"highlightWord\":\"night\",\"factType\":\"surprise\"},{\"text\":\"My white flesh is dotted with tiny black seeds!\",\"highlightWord\":\"seeds\",\"factType\":\"colour\"}],\"questions\":[{\"id\":\"dragon-fruit-q1\",\"type\":\"colour-match\",\"questionText\":\"What colour is my skin?\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"dragon-fruit-q1-a\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#FFD700\",\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"dragon-fruit-q1-b\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#FF69B4\",\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"dragon-fruit-q1-c\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#0077B6\",\"icon\":null}],\"correctOptionId\":\"dragon-fruit-q1-b\",\"explanationCorrect\":\"Yes! I 