n cool climates!\",\"highlightWord\":\"thorny\",\"factType\":\"growth\"},{\"text\":\"I am tart when raw but sweet when cooked in a pie!\",\"highlightWord\":\"pie\",\"factType\":\"surprise\"},{\"text\":\"I am rich in vitamin C and fibre!\",\"highlightWord\":\"vitamin\",\"factType\":\"nutrition\"}],\"questions\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q1\",\"type\":\"colour-match\",\"questionText\":\"What colour am I most commonly?\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q1-a\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#4CAF50\",\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q1-b\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#1a1a2e\",\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q1-c\",\"text\":null,\"colour\":\"#FF69B4\",\"icon\":null}],\"correctOptionId\":\"gooseberry-q1-a\",\"explanationCorrect\":\"Yes! I am most commonly green!\",\"explanationIncorrect\":\"Nearly! I am most commonly green!\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q2\",\"type\":\"where-grow\",\"questionText\":\"Where do I grow?\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q2-a\",\"text\":\"On a bush\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":\"🌿\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q2-b\",\"text\":\"On a vine\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":\"🌱\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q2-c\",\"text\":\"On a tree\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":\"🌳\"}],\"correctOptionId\":\"gooseberry-q2-a\",\"explanationCorrect\":\"Yes! I grow on a thorny bush!\",\"explanationIncorrect\":\"No, I actually grow on a thorny bush!\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q3\",\"type\":\"true-false\",\"questionText\":\"Gooseberries only grow in hot tropical climates\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q3-a\",\"text\":\"True\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q3-b\",\"text\":\"False\",\"colour\":null,\"icon\":null}],\"correctOptionId\":\"gooseberry-q3-b\",\"explanationCorrect\":\"Correct! I prefer cool climates!\",\"explanationIncorrect\":\"Actually, I prefer cool climates — not tropical ones!\"},{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4\",\"type\":\"odd-one-out\",\"questionText\":\"Which one does NOT grow on a bush?\",\"options\":[{\"id\":\"gooseberry-q4-a\",\"text\":\"Gooseberry\",\"colo